snippet.title: Leo The Firefighter Cat - Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Ready to be a hero and brave the dangers?

Meet Leo, the courageous firefighter cat, and help him on his exciting adventure as a junior recruit at the fire station! 
Take on missions that get trickier each time and climb the ranks with the guidance of Commander Nox. 

Don't worry, you're not alone!

Leo : The Firefighter Cat will release on PC, Nintendo Switch, PlayStation 5 and Xbox Series in 2024.

More information are coming soon.

#leothefirefightercat
